title: Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
description: Steps to reproduce:1. Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to a zip file.
OB: The zip file does not allow files with the same name under different directories to be stored.
EB: If you name the file with the same name in a different directory, it should be stored in the zip file without any issues.
SR: 1. Create multiple files with the same name but in different directories.2. Export these files to a zip file.3. Check if the files are stored correctly in the zip file.
